body:
Hi Giuseppe,



I am not able to reproduce the error that you are finding. I have however updated all your components to the latest version of Honeybee you can do this by downloading the latest components from Github - [https://github.com/mostaphaRoudsari/Honeybee/tree/master/userObjects](https://github.com/mostaphaRoudsari/Honeybee/tree/master/userObjects).



After updating all the components on my machine the simulation runs smoothly. Let me know if this GH file is what you want.



Best,



Anton
